name: bubble chartjs
format:
<style>
  .bg_rgba {
    background-attachment: float;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 530px 341px;
    width: 600px;
    height: 452px;
    background-position: 45px 65px;
    /*background-color: rgba(242, 84, 89, 1.0);*/

    background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25)), url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    /*padding: 10px;
  border: 1px solid black; */
  }
</style>

<body style="height: 100%; margin: 0">
  <div class=bg_rgba style="width:600px;">
    <canvas id="bubble-chart" width="600" height="452"></canvas>
  </div>


  <script>
    (function(scope) {
    var timer = setInterval(function() {
    if (!window.echarts) return;
    clearInterval(timer);
     
    var myData;
     
   // var chart = document.getElementById('chart21');
    //var myChart = echarts.init(chart);
    new Chart(document.getElementById("bubble-chart"), {
     
    type: 'bubble',
    data: {
      labels: "label",
      datasets: [
        {
          label: "LD152",
          backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 255, 0, 1.0)",
          borderColor: "#000",
          data: [
          	
          	{x: 1.9, y: 6.1, r: 10 }
          ]
        },
        {
        label: "LD153",
        backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 216, 0, 1.0)",
        borderColor: "#000",
        data: [
        
        {x: 5.4, y: 6.9, r: 10 }
        ]
        },
        {
        label: "SH107",
        backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 102, 102, 1.0)",
        borderColor: "#000",
        data: [
        
        {x: 2.4, y: 1.1, r: 10 }
        ]
        },
        {
        label: "SH110",
        backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 153, 51, 1.0)",
        borderColor: "#000",
        data: [
        
        {x: 3.1, y: 0.9, r: 10 }
        ]
        }, {
          label: ["SH111"], 
          backgroundColor: "rgba(72, 255, 70,1.0)",
          borderColor: "#000",
          data: [
          	
          	{x: 3.2, y: 1.8, r: 10 }
		  ]
        }
      ]
    },
    options: {
        legend: {
            display: true,
            labels: {
                fontColor: 'rgb(255, 99, 132)'
            }
        },
      title: {
        display: true,
        text: 'Hang vs Queue time'
      }, scales: {
        yAxes: [{ 
          ticks: { max: 9, min: 0},
          gridLines: {
          display: true ,
          color: "#FFFFFF"
          },
          scaleLabel: {
            display: true,
            labelString: "Hang time(m)"
          }
        }],
        xAxes: [{ 
          ticks: { max: 6, min: 0},
          gridLines: {
          display: true ,
          color: "#FFFFFF"
          },
          scaleLabel: {
            display: true,
            labelString: "Queue time(m)"
          }
        }]
      }
    }
});
   // });

 
    scope.$watch('msg', function (msg) { //watch for an incoming NR msg
     if (msg) {
        myData = msg;
      /*  myChart.resize({
        width: 400,
        height: 200
        }); */
      new Chart(document.getElementById("bubble-chart"), {
      
    type: 'bubble',
    data: {
      labels: "label",
      datasets: myData.payload
    },
    options: {
        legend: {
            display: true,
            labels: {
                fontColor: 'rgb(255, 99, 132)'
            }
        },
      title: {
        display: true,
        text: 'Hang vs Queue time'
      }, scales: {
        yAxes: [{ 
          ticks: { max: 9, min: 0},
          gridLines: {
          display: true ,
          color: "#FFFFFF"
          },
          scaleLabel: {
            display: true,
            labelString: "Hang time(m)"
          }
        }],
        xAxes: [{ 
          ticks: { max: 6, min: 0},
          gridLines: {
          display: true ,
          color: "#FFFFFF"
          },
          scaleLabel: {
            display: true,
            labelString: "Queue time(m)"
          }
        }]
      }
    }
});
       
        
        };
        });
        }, 100);
        })(scope);

  </script>
</body>

</html>

name: bubble data
